reviewText: Pentrex did a great job in putting this DVD together showing Santa Fe mainline railroading into L.A.

As with most Pentrex movies, this was a great two hour show, especially if you're into Santa Fe, Railroads in the San Bernardino/Los Angeles area, or like mid 1990s railroading.  I'd definitely give it a 5/5 rating and recommend it to all fans of the ATSF Railway.
